Description: Modern NVIDIA Settings Manager for Pop!_OS Cosmic
 nvcontrol is a comprehensive NVIDIA GPU control tool optimized for
 Pop!_OS with the COSMIC desktop environment.
 .
 Features optimized for COSMIC:
  * Native Wayland support via cosmic-randr
  * Digital Vibrance control (no nvidia-settings required)
  * VRR / G-SYNC configuration via cosmic-settings
  * HDR management with COSMIC compositor
  * GPU overclocking and power management
  * Fan curve control
  * Multi-monitor profile management
  * Container GPU passthrough support
 .
 Integrates with System76's NVIDIA drivers and COSMIC desktop.
